### Chicken Flow API - REST Client
### Variables: actualiza con tu token JWT después de hacer login

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = TU_TOKEN_AQUI

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUTH
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Registrar usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin Test",
  "email": "admin@chickenflow.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@chickenflow.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Ver perfil
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DASHBOARD
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Resumen del dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Módulos rápidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/quick-modules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GRANJAS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar granjas
GET {{baseUrl}}/farms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear granja
POST {{baseUrl}}/farms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Granja Las Palmas",
  "location": "Quimbaya, Quindío",
  "areaM2": 18,
  "zones": 3,
  "capacity": 144
}

###

### Ver opciones de granjas (para selects)
GET {{baseUrl}}/farms/options
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MÓDULO PILOTO - LOTES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar lotes piloto
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear lote piloto
POST {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "farmId": "farm-seed-001",
  "zone": "Zona 1",
  "birdsInitial": 24,
  "durationDays": 42,
  "startDate": "2026-06-13",
  "pricePollito": 3500,
  "priceIniciador": 95000,
  "priceFinalizador": 90000,
  "priceViruta": 15000,
  "priceVacunas": 80000,
  "costCalefaccion": 50000,
  "costTransporte": 30000,
  "costProcesamiento": 20000,
  "costEntrega": 25000,
  "priceSaleLb": 6500,
  "expectedWeightKg": 2.5,
  "expectedCarcassKg": 0.76,
  "observationsInitial": "Lote de prueba piloto"
}

###

### Detalle de lote (reemplaza LOT_ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar estado de lote
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "finalizado"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REGISTROS DIARIOS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar registros diarios del lote
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/daily-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear registro diario
POST {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/daily-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cyclDay": 1,
  "date": "2026-06-13",
  "birdsAliveStart": 24,
  "deadBirds": 0,
  "feedKg": 1.2,
  "feedType": "iniciador",
  "waterChanged": true,
  "temperatureMorning": 28,
  "temperatureAfternoon": 30,
  "observations": "Primer día del ciclo, buen comportamiento"
}

###

### Actualizar registro diario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pilot/daily-records/RECORD_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deadBirds": 1,
  "observations": "Se encontró un pollo muerto por aplastamiento"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REGISTROS SEMANALES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar registros semanales
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/weekly-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear registro semanal (pesaje)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/weekly-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekNumber": 1,
  "startDay": 1,
  "endDay": 7,
  "weighingDate": "2026-06-20",
  "bird1WeightG": 850,
  "bird2WeightG": 870,
  "bird3WeightG": 860,
  "bird4WeightG": 880,
  "bird5WeightG": 865,
  "feedConsumedKg": 8.4,
  "deadBirdsWeek": 0,
  "observations": "Primera semana, crecimiento normal"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REPORTES Y CÁLCULOS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Resumen del lote
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Reporte final del lote
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/lots/LOT_ID/final-report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Calcular alimento necesario
GET {{baseUrl}}/pilot/calculos/alimento/24?precioIniciador=95000&precioFinalizador=90000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Verificar viabilidad del lote
POST {{baseUrl}}/pilot/calculos/viabilidad
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cantidadPollitos": 24,
  "precioPollito": 3500,
  "priceIniciador": 95000,
  "priceFinalizador": 90000,
  "priceViruta": 15000,
  "priceVacunas": 80000,
  "costCalefaccion": 50000,
  "costTransporte": 30000,
  "costProcesamiento": 20000,
  "costEntrega": 25000,
  "priceSaleLb": 6500,
  "expectedWeightKg": 2.5,
  "expectedCarcassKg": 0.76
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PRODUCCIÓN MULTI-LOTE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Resumen de producción del día
GET {{baseUrl}}/production/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar registros de producción
GET {{baseUrl}}/production/daily-records?date=2026-06-13
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# INVENTARIO DE ALIMENTO
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Ver inventario
GET {{baseUrl}}/feed-inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Resumen de inventario
GET {{baseUrl}}/feed-inventory/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Registrar compra de alimento
POST {{baseUrl}}/feed-inventory/purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "farmId": "farm-seed-001",
  "feedType": "finalizador",
  "brand": "Engorde Plus 40kg",
  "quantityKg": 80,
  "unitCost": 90000,
  "storageLocation": "Bodega Norte · Tarro B",
  "expirationDate": "2026-08-18"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CLIENTES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar clientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Restaurante La Mesa",
  "document": "98765432",
  "phone": "3009876543",
  "city": "Armenia",
  "customerType": "restaurante",
  "creditLimit": 2000000
}

###

### Estado de cuenta del cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/CUSTOMER_ID/statement
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FACTURAS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar facturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUSTOMER_ID",
  "lotId": "LOT_ID",
  "issueDate": "2026-06-13",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-27",
  "chickensSold": 12,
  "totalWeightLb": 63.5,
  "pricePerLb": 7000,
  "paymentCondition": "credito_15_dias"
}

###

### Cambiar estado de factura
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoices/INVOICE_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "pagada"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PAGOS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Resumen de cobros
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Registrar pago
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INVOICE_ID",
  "amount": 200000,
  "paymentMethod": "transferencia",
  "paymentDate": "2026-06-14",
  "reference": "TRX-88912"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FINANZAS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Resumen financiero del mes
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/summary?period=2026-06
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Cierre de periodo financiero (solo admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/finance/close-period
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "period": "2026-06",
  "includeLots": ["LOT_ID"],
  "distributionRule": {
    "reinvestment": 60,
    "emergencyFund": 25,
    "dividends": 15,
    "founderShare": 80,
    "operatorShare": 20
  }
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# USUARIOS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar usuarios (solo admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Invitar usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "María Operadora",
  "email": "maria@chickenflow.com",
  "role": "operator",
  "farmId": "farm-seed-001"
}

###

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health
